      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education_ClassroomService项目画一个Git流程图，展示三条分支的结构，以及从每条分支上cherry-pick特定提交到main线的场景。标题就叫\"Three branches and a cherry-pick from each\"吧。",
