    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop和featureA两条线。具体来说，develop上要有A、B、C三个提交，featureA从develop分出后有FIX和FIX-2两个提交。然后main线从ZERO开始，依次有ONE、TWO、THREE，其中TWO之后要从develop cherry-pick提交A，THREE之后要从featureA cherry-pick提交FIX。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
