      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础结构：main从ZERO开始，分出develop后develop上有A，然后切回main做ONE，再回develop做B，这时候从develop分出featureA，featureA上做FIX和FIX-2。",
      "elements_involved": [
